<SYNC Start=957173><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=957214><P Class=KRCC>봐! 이거..
<SYNC Start=958553><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=958577><P Class=KRCC>앗! 탄로 났네
<SYNC Start=960205><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=961933><P Class=KRCC>뭐가! 뭐가! 뭐가 큰데..<br>뭐가 큰 거냐고! 뭐가..
<SYNC Start=965110><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=966189><P Class=KRCC>싫어! 무섭단 말야~
<SYNC Start=968434><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=970533><P Class=KRCC>조금 더 젖힌 상태였으면 좋겠구만..
<SYNC Start=973488><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=973489><P Class=KRCC>안 돼~ 안 돼~
<SYNC Start=977409><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=992643><P Class=KRCC>별꼴이야.. 별꼴이야
<SYNC Start=994443><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=994467><P Class=KRCC>못 봤어.. 못 봤어<br>나 못 봤다구
<SYNC Start=996435><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
