<SYNC Start=1951892><P Class=KRCC>싫어
<SYNC Start=1952900><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1965959><P Class=KRCC>부인! 미안해
<SYNC Start=1968059><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
