<SYNC Start=1970262><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1979754><P Class=KRCC>기분 좋지?
<SYNC Start=1980783><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1993613><P Class=KRCC>부인! 좋아?
<SYNC Start=1996238><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2007814><P Class=KRCC>기분 좋지? 부인.. 응?
<SYNC Start=2009599><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
